    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Try this:</p>\n\n<pre><code>CharSequence[] charArray = {\"a\",\"b\",\"c\"};\n\nfor (int i = 0; i &lt; charArray.length; i++){\n    String str = charArray.toString().join(\"\", charArray[i]);\n    System.out.print(str);\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
