    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<pre><code> //Given Character Array \n  char[] a = {'h', 'e', 'l', 'l', 'o', ' ', 'w', 'o', 'r', 'l', 'd'};\n\n\n    //Converting Character Array to String using String funtion     \n    System.out.println(String.valueOf(a));\n    //OUTPUT : hello world\n</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>Converting any given Array type to String using Java 8 Stream function</strong></p>\n\n<pre><code>String stringValue = \nArrays.stream(new char[][]{a}).map(String::valueOf).collect(Collectors.joining());\n</code></pre>\n"
